British Land in Talks to Buy Spain Shopping Mall, Expansion Says

-- B y   S h a r o n   S m y t h
-- 
2011-05-16T06:26:18Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-16/british-land-in-talks-to-buy-spain-shopping-mall-expansion-says.html
British Land Co. Plc is in talks to
buy a shopping mall in Toledo,  Spain , and will commence work on
the second phase of a retail park in Zaragoza,  Expansion 
reported, citing people with knowledge of the matter.  The U.K. company is discussing the purchase of the La
Abadia shopping mall in Toledo for 65 million euros ($92
million) and will start work on second stage for the Puerto
Venecia retail development in Zaragoza, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Sharon Smyth in Madrid at 
 ssmyth2@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew Blackman at   ablackman@bloomberg.net . 